Simple visualizer of the convex hull algorithm.

Make project: 
    git submodule update --init
    cd visualization
    (optionally rm PRECOMPILED_HEADER = stdafx.h in geom.visualization.pro)
    qmake && make
    cd ..
    qmake && make

Add point:           double click
Build convex hull:   press key 'Enter'
Save points:         press key 'S'
Load points:         press key 'L'

